{"tid":1662234,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【日常文宣】[推爆佢]本土國際戰線—Facebook","createTime":"2019-10-18T15:33:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T08:18:25.000Z","uid":307203,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"6f2360b1921637c6138fe5e637be091c7f96e58f","tid":1662234,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:33:20.000Z","msg":"巴打唔好意思 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望你唔好介意我抄你嘅post<br />\n<br />\n原post:【簡易文宣】本土戰線&mdash;FaceBook!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648722\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648722</a><br />\n<br />\n前言.<br />\n小弟覺得原post 只係集中於我哋嗰邊，但Facebook作為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">世界主流社交網站</span></span>，其實我哋同樣可以有Twitter同Reddit 一樣文宣效果，所以都要打埋呢一次戰線<br />\n<br />\n同埋要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">將文宣日常化先可以將效果變大</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但如果大家想加入其他國際文宣戰線，以下為加入方式<br />\n<br />\n1.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">Twitter</span></span> 共識channel <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9i%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=88a3d68c\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n<br />\n【突發】每晚十點 全民Twitter ！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656182\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656182</a><br />\n<br />\n2.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">Reddit</span></span> 文宣部 <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/redditmansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fredditmansyunzou&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9i%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=daec5051\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/redditmansyunzou</a><br />\n<br />\nReddit戰線要人！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656389\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656389</a><br />\n<br />\n3.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">英文文宣Channel</span></span>：<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo_int\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstandstrong_promo_int&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9i%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=91630c30\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo_int</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hkposter777\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkposter777&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9i%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=51dabe0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkposter777</a><br />\n<br />\n無論本土或國際戰線都係一個非常簡單嘅文宣方式，同埋你就算<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幾懶都好，你都一定有一個Facebook account</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n如果你怕被人用Facebook post 篤灰，你都可以開多一個account<br />\n<br />\n正文.<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">本士:</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">A.黃絲</span></span><br />\nFacebook其實喺和理非聚集地，係一個可以好好做文宣嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，想邀請大家一齊做<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好簡單 但喺成效大</span></span><br />\n<br />\n步驟/注意事項：<br />\n<br />\n1/ <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">搵啲出名嘅page</span></span><br />\n例如 立場 蘋果 獨媒 金水 大J 民安 天佑 等等<br />\n<br />\n或者中立同扮黄page <br />\n例如 明報 信報 01 經濟 Now 有線等<br />\n<br />\n總之要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全方位無死角</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n2/ <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">搵個新嘅post</span></span><br />\n例如<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0d6MOQc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0d6MOQc.png&h=ff8b21f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n越新嘅post效果越好<br />\n<br />\n3/ <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">留言擺文宣圖 然後自己like自己</span></span><br />\n例如<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k45qjXC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk45qjXC.png&h=377df145&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4/ <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">見到同路人擺文宣 記得要like返</span></span><br />\n好重要 因為得你一個自己like自己<br />\n曝光率好低<br />\n所以見到手足擺文宣圖記得要like<br />\n<br />\n5/ 遇到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武手足裝修</span></strong></span>的影片時<br />\n留言 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警自導自演 一定喺臥底！ 黑警辛苦曬啦</span></strong></span> 等等<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為fb嘅和理非好相信大部分勇武行動都喺狗做嘅</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要依個風向延續不斷 再加插啲解釋點解要裝修嘅文宣<br />\n例如<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3UEOhMA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3UEOhMA.jpg&h=73061ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我地唔會點失民意</span><br />\n<br />\n效果：<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.和理非遊行同行動人數大增</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">2.互相團結不分化</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">B.藍絲</span></strong></span><br />\n1.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">打破同温層</span></span><br />\n<br />\n拯救藍絲！正式進入：「Facebook連儂牆計劃」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1580225\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1580225</a><br />\n<br />\n2.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">Report</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n得閒就去report人哋， 總之搞到佢哋似點新聞咁樣死不翻生<br />\n例如以下立場報過嘅page<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E8%97%8D%E7%B5%B2%E8%87%89%E6%9B%B8%E5%B0%88%E9%A0%81%E5%8F%8A%E7%A4%BE%E7%BE%A4%E5%A4%A7%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88-fb-page-group/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%2597%258D%25E7%25B5%25B2%25E8%2587%2589%25E6%259B%25B8%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A0%2581%25E5%258F%258A%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%259B%2586%25E5%2590%2588-fb-page-group%2F&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9i%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=1b9d7f1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%2597%258D%25E7%25B5%25B2%25E8%2587%2589%25E6%259B%25B8%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A0%2581%25E5%258F%258A%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%259B%2586%25E5%2590%2588-fb-page-group%2F&h=ef5b3414\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E8%97%8D%E7%B5%B2%E8%87%89%E6%9B%B8%E5%B0%88%E9%A0%81%E5%8F%8A%E7%A4%BE%E7%BE%A4%E5%A4%A7%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88-fb-page-group/</a><br />\n<br />\n不過仲有好多嘅，總之大家見到就即刻report<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仇恨言論</span></span><br />\n同埋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TfUbGmP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTfUbGmP.png&h=909e76ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">分化對家</span></span><br />\n<br />\n既然人哋都不斷分化我哋， 點解我哋唔去分化人哋呢？<br />\n<br />\n我哋可以順便<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">開多個account去扮藍絲</span></strong></span>，分化對家同帶風向，搞到佢哋都要捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n可以參考以下post：<br />\n1.[品蔥建議] [拋磚引玉] 如何偽裝成一名合格的&ldquo;愛國港人&rdquo;（藍絲）？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648664\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648664</a><br />\n<br />\n2.[文宣] 手足們係時候分化班狗同冇腦藍絲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1237194\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1237194</a><br />\n<br />\n3. [香城OL新職業]【符號爭奪戰】誠招幻象師! 黃絲係我地; 藍絲? 都係我地!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1335220\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1335220</a><br />\n<br />\n4.［文宣升級］長輩式反攻保皇FB Page<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1223616\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1223616</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記得要用埋我哋嘅長輩圖去分化同反攻啊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">國際</span></span>:<br />\n1.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">上去國際傳媒、NGO同埋世界政客嘅page</span></span><br />\n<br />\n例如 BBC CNN ABC Foxnews 紐約時報 泰晤士報 國際特赦組織 Ted Cruz 蔡英文 等等<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">搵個新嘅有關香港嘅post</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">Like 同埋打留言或放文宣或者Meme圖</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n方向：<br />\n1.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港係自由世界嘅前線</span></span>， <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">係東方西柏林</span></span><br />\n例如：<br />\n美國國會議員將香港類比為冷戰高峰時期嘅西柏林！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1653833\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1653833</a><br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人道危機</span></span><br />\n例如：<br />\n（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a><br />\n<br />\n【國際線行動】應盡快整理612後警暴片段，同納粹暴行做對比，爭取西方實際行動支持香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">燒到埋身</span></span><br />\n總之要令到全世界都知<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中共會搞到佢哋利益受損同埋失去自由</span></span><br />\n<br />\n要製造出如同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">當年西方對蘇聯同納粹德國嘅恐懼</span></span><br />\n例如：<br />\n［國際文宣］用英文整合中共係國際各個層面唧控制 令外國人都會有身受其害嘅覺悟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1492342\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1492342</a><br />\n<br />\n最好要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">專注五毛出征嗰啲新聞</span></span><br />\n<br />\n例如NBA ( 通常都係雞毛蒜皮嘅小事)<br />\n<br />\n因為官方引導佢哋搞完嘢後，仲要叫官媒同埋外交部出嚟大聲譴責同恐嚇，通常都會搞出一個小型風波<br />\n<br />\n所以我哋嘅責任就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">將場火越燒越大</span></strong></span>，最好就係共產黨最後都要跪低，收番佢哋所講嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總結.<br />\n所以如果大家懶嘅話或者唔想開其他平台嘅account嘅話，請大家盡做Facebook 文宣"},{"pid":"3267928456ccd0f3716e9f207c043514327abaef","tid":1662234,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:34:03.000Z","msg":"十二十 尖咀見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec82a02cd1048964b38425300cee7b7865300b6b","tid":1662234,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:34:24.000Z","msg":"十二十 尖咀見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e34e35430b21f6f2a56a639a2e6ec39624e0819","tid":1662234,"uid":307203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:34:35.000Z","msg":"十二十 尖咀見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e4aaa0fdf26d0aac85abbbfda51a031eef9836","tid":1662234,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:34:45.000Z","msg":"十二十 尖咀見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/